{"tid":1597190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"“五大訴求, 缺一不可”------根本唔夠聚焦!!!       [重開]","createTime":"2019-09-27T00:28:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T02:19:43.000Z","uid":69291,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"cc973b4e25a460b0229049b7e88b928e81803886","tid":1597190,"uid":69291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T00:28:20.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">叫&ldquo;五大訴求, 缺一不可&rdquo;<br />\n前面唔該加多句<br />\n</div><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">立即實行雙普選<br />\nDual Universal Suffrage<br />\n</div></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">我地依家係爭取緊民主, 自由, 自治<br />\n而呢樣野一講就明, 係個制度有問題<br />\n唔好只係掛住打syndrome <br />\n唔根治制度既問題, 所有要求都係空談<br />\n呢件事未完, 已經講緊蒙面法<br />\n到時又要幾多手足流血?<br />\n真雙普選, 香港人當家作主<br />\n只有咁樣我地先可以兌現係煲底相見既約定<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">港人治港, 驅逐共黨<br />\n光復香港, 時代革命<br />\n</span></span><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9 27<br />\n新屋嶺被捕者人權集會<br />\n日期: 9月27日 (星期五)<br />\n時間: 晚上7時30分<br />\n地點: 中環愛丁堡廣場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n9 28<br />\n民陣集會<br />\n日期: 9月28日 (星期六)<br />\n時間: 晚上7時<br />\n地點: 金鐘添馬公園<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n9 29<br />\n全球抗共遊行<br />\n日期: 9月29日 (星期日)<br />\n時間: 下午2時30分<br />\n起點: 銅鑼灣Sogo<br />\n終點: 金鐘政總<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n9 30<br />\n全港三罷<br />\n日期: 9月30日 (星期一)<br />\n罷工罷課罷市罷買 全港死城<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n10 1<br />\n如黨鐵正常營運<br />\n民陣遊行<br />\n日期: 10月1日 (星期二)<br />\n時間: 下午2時30分<br />\n起點: 銅鑼灣維園<br />\n終點: 中環遮打道<br />\n<br />\n如黨鐵封香港島<br />\n地區集會<br />\n日期: 10月1日 (星期二)<br />\n時間: 下午2時30分<br />\n地點: 各區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i5CaDmA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi5CaDmA.jpg&h=648eb52f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />瞓夠再重開<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同各位講多聲唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />麻煩認同既手足幫手推同埋到持帶頭嗌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />今晚見<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div>"},{"pid":"e10f3fb72982df5eaa38c368e08797fe8b7ae6f0","tid":1597190,"uid":69291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T00:28:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">WHAT WE NEED</span>"},{"pid":"18056841564a121d176acdd2943a1208b43acb84","tid":1597190,"uid":69291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T00:29:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">DUAL UNIVERSAL SUFFRAGE<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"4fb20bb28d98aef02ff353315a7f7972c62be20f","tid":1597190,"uid":69291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T00:29:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 立即實行</span>"},{"pid":"0fc04e27b38e4bc371befbe01b9517454b7b0df6","tid":1597190,"uid":69291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T00:29:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">雙普選</span>"},{"pid":"009b29e799a3e0d74dc82b3ca9e6e8507a284f5c","tid":1597190,"uid":167956,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T00:30:28.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n雙普選<br />\n有左就自然搞得成<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77d6d5d7b26a885053336e72387cb1b8028ab048","tid":1597190,"uid":4396,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T00:30:43.000Z","msg":"你係咪睇唔明五大訴求？義士唔係condom<img src=\"/as